{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.1","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:1","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.017.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h2 class=\"ms1\">LES DERNIERS ROIS DE JUDA, DEPUIS \u00c9Z\u00c9CHIAS JUSQU\u2019\u00c0 LA DESTRUCTION DU ROYAUME DE JUDA<\/h2>\n<h3 class=\"mr\">Ch. 18 \u00e0 25. (2 Ch 29 \u00e0 36.) (J\u00e9 3:8-10. Am 2:4-5. So 3:1-4.)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. 2 Ch 29 \u00e0 31. Ps 119:1-3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La troisi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Os\u00e9e, fils d\u2019\u00c9la, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, \u00c9z\u00e9chias, fils d\u2019Achaz, roi de Juda, r\u00e9gna.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.2","name":"2 Rois 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.17.41","name":"2 Rois 17:41","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.17.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.2","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:2","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il avait vingt-cinq ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna vingt-neuf ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Abi, fille de Zacharie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.3","name":"2 Rois 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.1","name":"2 Rois 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.3","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:3","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, enti\u00e8rement comme avait fait David, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.4","name":"2 Rois 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.2","name":"2 Rois 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.4","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:4","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il fit dispara\u00eetre les hauts lieux, brisa les statues, abattit les idoles, et mit en pi\u00e8ces le serpent d\u2019airain que Mo\u00efse avait fait, car les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl avaient jusqu\u2019alors br\u00fbl\u00e9 des parfums devant lui: on l\u2019appelait Nehuschtan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.5","name":"2 Rois 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.3","name":"2 Rois 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.5","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:5","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il mit sa confiance en l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; et parmi tous les rois de Juda qui vinrent apr\u00e8s lui ou qui le pr\u00e9c\u00e9d\u00e8rent, il n\u2019y en eut point de semblable \u00e0 lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.6","name":"2 Rois 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.4","name":"2 Rois 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.6","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:6","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il fut attach\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, il ne se d\u00e9tourna point de lui, et il observa les commandements que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait prescrits \u00e0 Mo\u00efse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.7","name":"2 Rois 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.5","name":"2 Rois 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.7","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:7","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut avec \u00c9z\u00e9chias, qui r\u00e9ussit dans toutes ses entreprises. Il se r\u00e9volta contre le roi d\u2019Assyrie, et ne lui fut plus assujetti.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.8","name":"2 Rois 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.6","name":"2 Rois 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.8","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:8","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il battit les Philistins jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Gaza, et ravagea leur territoire depuis les tours des gardes jusqu\u2019aux villes fortes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.9","name":"2 Rois 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.7","name":"2 Rois 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.9","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:9","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-12: cf. 2 R 17:1-23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\n    La quatri\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias, qui \u00e9tait la septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Os\u00e9e, fils d\u2019\u00c9la, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Salmanasar, roi d\u2019Assyrie, monta contre Samarie et l\u2019assi\u00e9gea.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.10","name":"2 Rois 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.8","name":"2 Rois 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.10","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:10","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il la prit au bout de trois ans, la sixi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias, qui \u00e9tait la neuvi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Os\u00e9e, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: alors Samarie fut prise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.11","name":"2 Rois 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.9","name":"2 Rois 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.11","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:11","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Assyrie emmena Isra\u00ebl captif en Assyrie, et il les \u00e9tablit \u00e0 Chalach, et sur le Chabor, fleuve de Gozan, et dans les villes des M\u00e8des,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.12","name":"2 Rois 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.10","name":"2 Rois 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.12","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:12","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>parce qu\u2019ils n\u2019avaient point \u00e9cout\u00e9 la voix de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, leur Dieu, et qu\u2019ils avaient transgress\u00e9 son alliance, parce qu\u2019ils n\u2019avaient ni \u00e9cout\u00e9 ni mis en pratique tout ce qu\u2019avait ordonn\u00e9 Mo\u00efse, serviteur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.13","name":"2 Rois 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.11","name":"2 Rois 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.13","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:13","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le royaume de Juda envahi par Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie, et J\u00e9rusalem assi\u00e9g\u00e9e<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-16: cf. 2 Ch 32:1-8. (\u00c9s 7:17-25; 10:5-7, 28-32. Mi 1:8, etc.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\n    La quatorzi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias, Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie, monta contre toutes les villes fortes de Juda, et s\u2019en empara.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.14","name":"2 Rois 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.12","name":"2 Rois 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.14","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:14","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda, envoya dire au roi d\u2019Assyrie \u00e0 Lakis: J\u2019ai commis une faute! \u00c9loigne-toi de moi. Ce que tu m\u2019imposeras, je le supporterai. Et le roi d\u2019Assyrie imposa \u00e0 \u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda, trois cents talents d\u2019argent et trente talents d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.15","name":"2 Rois 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.13","name":"2 Rois 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.15","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:15","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias donna tout l\u2019argent qui se trouvait dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et dans les tr\u00e9sors de la maison du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.16","name":"2 Rois 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.14","name":"2 Rois 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.16","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:16","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Ce fut alors qu\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda, enleva, pour les livrer au roi d\u2019Assyrie, les lames d\u2019or dont il avait couvert les portes et les linteaux du temple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.17","name":"2 Rois 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.15","name":"2 Rois 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.17","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:17","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-37: cf. \u00c9s 36. 2 Ch 32:9-19. Ps 22:8-12. Mt 27:43.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Assyrie envoya de Lakis \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, vers le roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias, Tharthan, Rab-Saris et Rabschak\u00e9 avec une puissante arm\u00e9e. Ils mont\u00e8rent, et ils arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Lorsqu\u2019ils furent mont\u00e9s et arriv\u00e9s, ils s\u2019arr\u00eat\u00e8rent \u00e0 l\u2019aqueduc de l\u2019\u00e9tang sup\u00e9rieur, sur le chemin du champ du foulon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.18","name":"2 Rois 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.16","name":"2 Rois 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.18","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:18","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Ils appel\u00e8rent le roi; et \u00c9liakim, fils de Hilkija, chef de la maison du roi, se rendit aupr\u00e8s d\u2019eux, avec Schebna, le secr\u00e9taire, et Joach, fils d\u2019Asaph, l\u2019archiviste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.19","name":"2 Rois 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.17","name":"2 Rois 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.19","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:19","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Rabschak\u00e9 leur dit: Dites \u00e0 \u00c9z\u00e9chias: Ainsi parle le grand roi, le roi d\u2019Assyrie: Quelle est cette confiance, sur laquelle tu t\u2019appuies?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.20","name":"2 Rois 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.18","name":"2 Rois 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.20","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:20","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Tu as dit: Il faut pour la guerre de la prudence et de la force. Mais ce ne sont que des paroles en l\u2019air. En qui donc as-tu plac\u00e9 ta confiance, pour t\u2019\u00eatre r\u00e9volt\u00e9 contre moi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.21","name":"2 Rois 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.19","name":"2 Rois 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.21","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:21","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Voici, tu l\u2019as plac\u00e9e dans l\u2019\u00c9gypte, tu as pris pour soutien ce roseau cass\u00e9, qui p\u00e9n\u00e8tre et perce la main de quiconque s\u2019appuie dessus: tel est Pharaon, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte, pour tous ceux qui se confient en lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.22","name":"2 Rois 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.20","name":"2 Rois 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.22","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:22","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Peut-\u00eatre me direz-vous: C\u2019est en l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, que nous nous confions. Mais n\u2019est-ce pas lui dont \u00c9z\u00e9chias a fait dispara\u00eetre les hauts lieux et les autels, en disant \u00e0 Juda et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem: Vous vous prosternerez devant cet autel \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.23","name":"2 Rois 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.21","name":"2 Rois 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.23","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:23","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Maintenant, fais une convention avec mon ma\u00eetre, le roi d\u2019Assyrie, et je te donnerai deux mille chevaux, si tu peux fournir des cavaliers pour les monter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.24","name":"2 Rois 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.22","name":"2 Rois 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.24","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:24","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Comment repousserais-tu un seul chef d\u2019entre les moindres serviteurs de mon ma\u00eetre? Tu mets ta confiance dans l\u2019\u00c9gypte pour les chars et pour les cavaliers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.25","name":"2 Rois 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.23","name":"2 Rois 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.25","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:25","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>D\u2019ailleurs, est-ce sans la volont\u00e9 de l\u2019\u00c9ternel que je suis mont\u00e9 contre ce lieu, pour le d\u00e9truire? L\u2019\u00c9ternel m\u2019a dit: Monte contre ce pays, et d\u00e9truis-le.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.26","name":"2 Rois 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.24","name":"2 Rois 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.26","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:26","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>\u00c9liakim, fils de Hilkija, Schebna et Joach, dirent \u00e0 Rabschak\u00e9: Parle \u00e0 tes serviteurs en aram\u00e9en, car nous le comprenons; et ne nous parle pas en langue juda\u00efque, aux oreilles du peuple qui est sur la muraille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.27","name":"2 Rois 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.25","name":"2 Rois 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.27","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:27","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Rabschak\u00e9 leur r\u00e9pondit: Est-ce \u00e0 ton ma\u00eetre et \u00e0 toi que mon ma\u00eetre m\u2019a envoy\u00e9 dire ces paroles? N\u2019est-ce pas \u00e0 ces hommes assis sur la muraille pour manger leurs excr\u00e9ments et pour boire leur urine avec vous?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.28","name":"2 Rois 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.26","name":"2 Rois 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.28","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:28","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Alors Rabschak\u00e9, s\u2019\u00e9tant avanc\u00e9, cria \u00e0 haute voix en langue juda\u00efque, et dit: \u00c9coutez la parole du grand roi, du roi d\u2019Assyrie!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.29","name":"2 Rois 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.27","name":"2 Rois 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.29","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:29","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Ainsi parle le roi: Qu\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias ne vous abuse point, car il ne pourra vous d\u00e9livrer de ma main.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.30","name":"2 Rois 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.28","name":"2 Rois 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.30","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:30","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Qu\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias ne vous am\u00e8ne point \u00e0 vous confier en l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en disant: L\u2019\u00c9ternel nous d\u00e9livrera, et cette ville ne sera pas livr\u00e9e entre les mains du roi d\u2019Assyrie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.31","name":"2 Rois 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.29","name":"2 Rois 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.31","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:31","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>N\u2019\u00e9coutez point \u00c9z\u00e9chias; car ainsi parle le roi d\u2019Assyrie: Faites la paix avec moi, rendez-vous \u00e0 moi, et chacun de vous mangera de sa vigne et de son figuier, et chacun boira de l\u2019eau de sa citerne,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.32","name":"2 Rois 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.30","name":"2 Rois 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.32","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:32","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que je vienne, et que je vous emm\u00e8ne dans un pays comme le v\u00f4tre, dans un pays de bl\u00e9 et de vin, un pays de pain et de vignes, un pays d\u2019oliviers \u00e0 huile et de miel, et vous vivrez et vous ne mourrez point. N\u2019\u00e9coutez donc point \u00c9z\u00e9chias; car il pourrait vous s\u00e9duire en disant: L\u2019\u00c9ternel nous d\u00e9livrera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.33","name":"2 Rois 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.31","name":"2 Rois 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.33","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:33","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Les dieux des nations ont-ils d\u00e9livr\u00e9 chacun son pays de la main du roi d\u2019Assyrie?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.34","name":"2 Rois 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.32","name":"2 Rois 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.34","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:34","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>O\u00f9 sont les dieux de Hamath et d\u2019Arpad? O\u00f9 sont les dieux de Sepharva\u00efm, d\u2019H\u00e9na et d\u2019Ivva? Ont-ils d\u00e9livr\u00e9 Samarie de ma main?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.35","name":"2 Rois 18:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.33","name":"2 Rois 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.35","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:35","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Parmi tous les dieux de ces pays, quels sont ceux qui ont d\u00e9livr\u00e9 leur pays de ma main, pour que l\u2019\u00c9ternel d\u00e9livre J\u00e9rusalem de ma main?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.36","name":"2 Rois 18:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.34","name":"2 Rois 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.36","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:36","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Le peuple se tut, et ne lui r\u00e9pondit pas un mot; car le roi avait donn\u00e9 cet ordre: Vous ne lui r\u00e9pondrez pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.37","name":"2 Rois 18:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.35","name":"2 Rois 18:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.37","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 18:37","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.018.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.18.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Et \u00c9liakim, fils de Hilkija, chef de la maison du roi, Schebna, le secr\u00e9taire, et Joach, fils d\u2019Asaph, l\u2019archiviste, vinrent aupr\u00e8s d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias, les v\u00eatements d\u00e9chir\u00e9s, et lui rapport\u00e8rent les paroles de Rabschak\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18","name":"2 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.19.1","name":"2 Rois 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.36","name":"2 Rois 18:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.18.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+documen